# generated/ — AI-derived artifacts (code maps, summaries, snapshots).
# 
# Lifecycle:
#   - Overwrite when regenerated.
#   - Never source-of-truth.
#   - Must remain reproducible from current code + context.
# 
# Commit policy:
#   - Default gitignored (see /.gitignore at repo root).
#   - Commit ONLY if: stable, useful across sessions, reproducible.
#   - Every file MUST have `source: ai` and non-authoritative status.
